title: 113 - Zito's Return From The Covid Cave
description: On today's show, Zito is back from the covid cave and he breaks down everything he watched and ate during his quarantine, and they get into a loaded Pod FOD that includes Vin Diesel having a revelation about the ending of the Fast and Furious franchise, John Cena getting a spinoff series about The Peacemaker, a children's show in Denmark about a man with a magical penis getting some blowback, 8 gorillas at the San Diego Zoo who have covid, Big Motor is also back from his covid cave, and much much more. Don't forget to send your questions into the Pod FOD @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram. We appreciate you all, we'll see you Friday.
